recode|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
recode: recode (Conversion between character sets and surfaces)
recode:
recode: The `recode' converts files between character sets and usages.
recode: It recognises or produces nearly 150 different character sets and
recode: is able to transliterate files between almost any pair. When exact
recode: transliteration are not possible, it may get rid of the offending
recode: characters or fall back on approximations. Most RFC 1345 character
recode: sets are supported.
recode:
recode: http://recode.progiciels-bpi.ca/
recode: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
